OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780736731
OL,3,CISS astronauts told to prepare for
OL,4,Cpossible evacuation over air leak
OL,6,FAstronauts on the International Space
OL,7,FStation have been told to take shelter
OL,8,Fin their spacecraft and prepare for a
OL,9,Fpotential evacuation due to a
OL,10,Fworsening air leak on the Russian
OL,11,FOrbital Segment, Nasa has said.
OL,13,FFour members of Nasa's SpaceX Crew-12
OL,14,Fand an additional astronaut were told
OL,15,Fto board the Dragon spacecraft and
OL,16,F"assume an elevated safety posture"
OL,17,Fwhile Roscosmos - Russia's space
OL,18,Fagency - works on repairs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
