CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780736731
OL,3,CISS astronauts told to prepare for
OL,4,Cpossible evacuation over air leak
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"The Zvezda service module transfer
OL,12,Ftunnel, known as PrK, has suffered
OL,13,Ffrom cracks and leaks for some time,
OL,14,Fand has been mitigated by Roscosmos as
OL,15,Fmuch as possible to date," Nasa
OL,16,Fspokesperson Bethany Stevens said on
OL,17,FFriday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780736731
OL,3,CISS astronauts told to prepare for
OL,4,Cpossible evacuation over air leak
OL,6,FThe cracks have always been a concern
OL,7,Fthat "Nasa watches very closely",
OL,8,FStevens continued, adding that it had
OL,9,Fbeen working with Roscosmos to
OL,10,Fdetermine the root cause of the cracks.
OL,12,F"Roscosmos manages the issue through
OL,13,Foperational mitigation measures and
OL,14,Fperiodic partial-repair efforts,"
OL,15,FStevens said.
OL,17,F"Following new leaks, Roscosmos has
OL,18,Felected to proceed with a more
OL,19,Fextensive repair operation on Friday,
OL,20,FJune 5.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
