PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780736731
OL,3,CISS astronauts told to prepare for
OL,4,Cpossible evacuation over air leak
OL,6,F"Out of an abundance of caution, Nasa
OL,7,Fhas directed all four of the agency's
OL,8,FSpaceX Crew-12 members and NASA
OL,9,Fastronaut Chris Williams to assume an
OL,10,Felevated safety posture in the Dragon
OL,11,Fspacecraft while the repair is
OL,12,Funderway."
OL,14,FThe 12th SpaceX crew of four is made
OL,15,Fup of US astronauts Jessica Meir and
OL,16,FJack Hathaway, French astronaut Sophie
OL,17,FAdenot of the European Space Agency
OL,18,Fand Andrey Fedyaev, from Roscosmos.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
